The static library 'libtz_drv_bc' is a TA library which provide the APIs to access external memory interface function in MTK in-house TEE.


WHAT IT DOES?
=============

The 'libtz_drv_bc' provides the API to access external memory interface function inside MTK in-house TEE.


HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'vendor/mediatek/libs' folder.


HOW TO USE IT?
==============

The libary 'libtz_drv_bc' is linked with the image of MTK in-house TEE.
It will be used to access emi function.

All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..
